I agree that this will work but I&#39;d prefer not to put the onus on 
every test author to remember to set the magic cleanUp flag.

I&#39;m going to experiment with my own TestRunner that simply overrides 
these methods:

	public void addError(Test test, Throwable t);
 	public void addFailure(Test test, AssertionFailedError t);  

I&#39;ll let you know how it goes.

Thanks!

